{"tid":2259594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梧桐河放生成災 死魚傳惡臭","createTime":"2020-10-27T03:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T03:21:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac77010319fdbdd687e82663d2acc525e62b15e","tid":2259594,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:09:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/3MIQDW3OSRAXPJHR6GBWRDWLHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2F3MIQDW3OSRAXPJHR6GBWRDWLHQ%2F&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETZNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=61a7a226\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2F3MIQDW3OSRAXPJHR6GBWRDWLHQ%2F&h=dee0d41f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/3MIQDW3OSRAXPJHR6GBWRDWLHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n梧桐河放生成災 死魚傳惡臭<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】佛教及道教等宗教相信放生可以積福，但胡亂放生或會害死動物，放生變成殺生。上水梧桐河一向是放生熱點，有村民投訴河流近年不斷湧現大量死魚，更傳出惡臭，惟向多個部門投訴均無果，慨嘆「根本冇條例監管」。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者昨早與村民來到梧桐河視察，記者所見，河內有近千條魚，包括不常在河內生活的錦鯉。視察期間記者發現兩名女士推着一架手推車，車上擺放田雞、生魚等大量魚類、海鮮，其中一名黃姓女士否認到場放生，惟多次改口，開初稱該批海鮮是「自己食」，其後又改稱到街市送貨。<br />\n<br />\n手推車上除存放泥鰍膠袋內有水外，其餘均沒用水存放魚類。有市民報警，斥。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/A_5oCSMjIgxNtMD1lRQLqPZonqQ=/3543x2362/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FIKVYMZ5UFFVLDIX5COXQYACJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FA_5oCSMjIgxNtMD1lRQLqPZonqQ%3D%2F3543x2362%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFIKVYMZ5UFFVLDIX5COXQYACJM.jpg&h=1ab52d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■上水梧桐河是放生熱點，河內有近千條魚，包括不常在河內生活的錦鯉。許頌明攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n村民多次投訴不果<br />\n<br />\n居於梧桐河附近的村民Tom指，近年經常有大量死魚浮在河面，更傳岀異味，「唔係一車車咁買、擺落河就得，（被放生的魚類）根本唔。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n村民梁先生曾向多個部門投訴，警方回覆稱放生行動不能證明虐畜，魚亦非垃圾，不能以亂拋垃圾為由執法；渠務署稱只會勸喻市民遠離河道。梁先生慨嘆「根本冇條例監管」。<br />\n<br />\n漁護署表示，過去半年未接獲有關於梧桐河放生魚類的投訴，但會就事件巡查相關地點，查。。。。。。。。。，有關法例最高刑罰為監禁三年及罰款20萬元。<br />\n<br />\n渠務署回覆曾接獲梧桐河放生魚類投訴，。。。。。。。。。。。間共收到四宗涉及梧桐河放生魚類的污染投訴，曾派員到場調查，只發現少量死魚，已聯絡渠務署清理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DPJ7eluhVtjUoMBZSPkPdRz3UtY=/1268x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5YFDONLZIFEXNP46HHJQRHSQ4I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDPJ7eluhVtjUoMBZSPkPdRz3UtY%3D%2F1268x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5YFDONLZIFEXNP46HHJQRHSQ4I.jpg&h=9cfe9cb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■田雞是放生熱門動物之一。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9MdNnGBs3isW2ltlBloXtKhI0F0=/1287x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JWVGZY2XAZE27EY2XB35MZROW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9MdNnGBs3isW2ltlBloXtKhI0F0%3D%2F1287x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJWVGZY2XAZE27EY2XB35MZROW4.jpg&h=1663b23c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有人疑帶魚類到梧桐河放生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2joNF80N4jL4qikCXMMIcwXLMiw=/2337x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LQTR2VVM2RFKDHVVMZWOE5UIEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2joNF80N4jL4qikCXMMIcwXLMiw%3D%2F2337x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLQTR2VVM2RFKDHVVMZWOE5UIEY.jpg&h=d8d159d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■現場有大量死魚傳出惡臭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bsCHML1Jks4Re1bGUROI9xQs_cg=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BMUAWIDPD5D3RHGWAF5EDPXC5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbsCHML1Jks4Re1bGUROI9xQs_cg%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBMUAWIDPD5D3RHGWAF5EDPXC5Y.jpg&h=3f5e655f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有女士推着擺放田雞、生魚等大量海鮮的手推車到場，被警員帶署調查。"},{"pid":"1a7fa4279815e7fbc9d9d17bd07ca15688a3c9ed","tid":2259594,"uid":231583,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:12:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"162b4445195b468489cba0d1ecdff19871d7e516","tid":2259594,"uid":381265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a7fa4279815e7fbc9d9d17bd07ca15688a3c9ed","tid":2259594,"uid":231583,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:12:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"笑到我停唔到"},{"pid":"09bb784e8dad6480f73e94ca755089f347e0437a","tid":2259594,"uid":76063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a7fa4279815e7fbc9d9d17bd07ca15688a3c9ed","tid":2259594,"uid":231583,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:12:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:15:51.000Z","msg":"好耐冇見呢張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7c0d2c61db260322f190743a606a9e4dca5503","tid":2259594,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:18:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d94ed19905ff93b2e5ea820db6f23e34c6b9e43","tid":2259594,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a7fa4279815e7fbc9d9d17bd07ca15688a3c9ed","tid":2259594,"uid":231583,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:12:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 